.env.*
*.key
*.pem
**/secrets/

# Logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# Test
coverage/

# Sub-projects (separate repos)
website/
_reference-site/

# Symlinks to personal content
media

# Soma local memory (override: .soma/STATE.md and .soma/protocols/ ARE tracked via negation)
!.soma/STATE.md
!.soma/protocols/
!.soma/protocols/**
!.soma/plans/
!.soma/plans/**

# Git worktrees (feature branches checked out side-by-side)
.worktrees/
